re, England, United Kingdom":"英国英格兰越可爾希可萊頓","lifeSummary":"Jacobina Middleton于1393年出生在英国維斯特莫藍德。她于1403年与Thomas Jenkes在英国英格兰巴金哈姆爾沃爾維頓结婚。他们至少是1个儿子的父母。她去世于1435年在英国維斯特莫藍德普雷斯頓 帕特里克享年42岁。"},"hr":{"1393–1435":"1393.–1435.","1395–1435":"1395–1435.","1382–1429":"1382–1429.","1431–1523":"1431.–1523","1434–Male":"1434.–preminuo","1414–1459":"1414.–1459","1459":"1459","1403":"1403.","1414":"1414.","1435":"1435.","1523":"1523","1434":"1434.","1431":"1431.","1395":"1395","1393":"1393.","1382":"1382","1429":"1429.","Wolverton, Buckinghamshire, England":"Wolverton, Buckinghamshire, England","Westmorland, England":"Westmorland, England","Preston Patrick, Westmorland, England":"Preston Patrick, Westmorland, England","Hickleton, Yorkshire, England, United Kingdom":"Hickleton, Yorkshire, Engleska, United Kingdom"},"cs":{"1393–1435":"1393–1435","1395–1435":"1395–1435","1382–1429":"1382–1429","1431–1523":"1431–1523","1434–Male":"1434–Zesnulý","1414–1459":"1414–1459","1459":"1459","1403":"1403","1414":"1414","1435":"1435","1523":"1523","1434":"1434","1431":"1431","1395":"1395","1393":"1393","1382":"1382","1429":"1429","Wolverton, Buckinghamshire, England":"Wolverton, Buckinghamshire, Anglie","Westmorland, England":"Westmorland, Anglie","Preston Patrick, Westmorland, England":"Preston Patrick, Westmorland, Anglie","Hickleton, Yorkshire, England, United Kingdom":"Hickleton, Yorkshire, Anglie, United Kingdom"},"da":{"1393–1435":"1393–1435","1395–1435":"1395–1435","1382–1429":"1382–1429","1431–1523":"1431–1523","1434–Male":"1434–Afdød","1414–1459":"1414–1459","1459":"1459","1403":"1403","1414":"1414","1435":"1435","1523":"1523","1434":"1434","1431":"1431","1395":"1395","1393":"1393","1382":"1382","1429":"1429","Wolverton, Buckinghamshire, England":"Wolverton, Buckinghamshire, England","Westmorland, England":"Westmorland, England","Preston Patrick, Westmorland, England":"Preston Patrick, Westmorland, England","Hickleton, Yorkshire, England, United Kingdom":"Hickleton, Jórvík, England, United Kingdom"},"nl":{"1393–1435":"1393–1435","1395–1435":"1395–1435","1382–1429":"1382–1429","1431–1523":"1431–1523","1434–Male":"1434–Overleden","1414–1459":"1414–1459","1459":"1459","1403":"1403","1414":"1414","1435":"1435","1523":"1523","1434":"1434","1431":"1431","1395":"1395","1393":"1393","1382":"1382","1429":"1429","Wolverton, Buckinghamshire, England":"Wolverton, Buckinghamshire, England","Westmorland, England":"Westmorland, England","Preston Patrick, Westmorland, England":"Preston Patrick, Westmorland, England","Hickleton, Yorkshire, England, United Kingdom":"Hickleton, Yorkshire, Engeland, Verenigd Koninkrijk"},"en":{"1393–1435":"1393–1435","1395–1435":"1395–1435","1382–1429":"1382–1429","1431–1523":"1431–1523","1434–Male":"1434–Deceased","1414–1459":"1414–1459","1459":"1459","1403":"1403","1414":"1414","1435":"1435","1523":"1523","1434":"1434","1431":"1431","1395":"1395","1393":"1393","1382":"1382","1429":"1429","Wolverton, Buckinghamshire, England":"Wolverton, Buckinghamshire, England","Westmorland, England":"Westmorland, England","Preston Patrick, Westmorland, England":"Preston Patrick, Westmorland, England","Hickleton, Yorkshire, England, United Kingdom":"Hickleton, Yorkshire, England, United Kingdom","nameMeanings":[{"name":"Middleton","type":"LAST","attribution":"Dictionary of American Family Names © Patrick Hanks 2003, 2006.","meanings":["English: habitational name from any of the places so called. In over thirty instances from many different areas, the name is from Old English <i>midel</i> ‘middle’ + <i>tūn</i> ‘enclosure, settlement’. However, Middleton on the Hill near Leominster in Herefordshire appears in Domesday Book as <i>Miceltune</i>, the first element clearly being Old English <i>micel</i> ‘large’, ‘great’ (see   Middlebrook  ). Middleton Baggot and Middleton Priors in Shropshire have early spellings that suggest <i>gem̄thhyll</i> (from <i>gem̄th</i> ‘confluence’ + <i>hyll</i> ‘hill’) + <i>tūn</i> as the origin. This surname is also found in Scotland and Ireland.","History: A Scottish family of this name derives it from lands at Middleto(u)n near Kincardine. The Scottish physician Peter Middleton practiced in New York City after 1752 and was one of the founders of the medical school at King's College (now Columbia University) in 1767. One of the earliest of the Charleston, SC, Middleton family of prominent legislators was Arthur Middleton, born in Charleston in 1681. The name has also been established in Ireland since at least the 13th century; its presence was reinforced by settlers in the 17th century."],"variants":[{"name":"Midthun","meanings":["Norwegian: habitational name from any of about ten farmsteads in western Norway named Midtun, from Old Norse <i>mith</i> ‘middle’ + <i>tún</i> ‘enclosure, farmstead’. Compare   Middleton  ."]},{"name":"Melton","meanings":["English (northern): habitational name from any of various places, for example in Leicestershire, Lincolnshire, Norfolk, and Yorkshire, all of which have the same origin as   Middleton  , with Old English <i>middel</i> replaced by its Old Norse equivalent <i>methal</i> after the Scandinavian settlement of northern and eastern England."]},{"name":"Middlebrook","meanings":["English: habitational name from a lost <i>Micklebrook</i> in Blackburn (Lancashire), recorded as <i>Mikelbroc</i> in the 13th century. The placename appears to derive from Old English <i>micel</i> ‘big’ + <i>brōc</i> ‘brook, stream’. The surname has undergone a dissimilatory or folk-etymological change from <i>Mickle-</i> to <i>Middle-</i>."]},{"name":"Milton","meanings":["English and Scottish: habitational name from one or other of the many places called Milton, or sometimes Middleton (see   Middleton  ) and occasionally Melton (see   Melton  ), most of which derive from Old English <i>middel</i> ‘middle’ or <i>myln</i> ‘mill’ + <i>tūn</i> ‘farmstead, estate’."]}]},{"name":"Jacobina","type":"FIRST","meanings":["A Scottish female name formed from Jacoba."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Jacobina Middleton was born in 1393, in Westmorland, England. She married Thomas Jenkes in 1403, in Wolverton, Buckinghamshire, England, United Kingdom. They were the parents of at least 1 son. She died in 1435, in Preston Patrick, Westmorland, England, at the age of 42."},"et":{"1393–1435":"1393–1435","1395–1435":"1395–1435","1382–1429":"1382–1429","1431–1523":"1431–1523","1434–Male":"1434–Surnud","1414–1459":"1414–1459","1459":"1459","1403":"1403","1414":"1414","1435":"1435","1523":"1523","1434":"1434","1431":"1431","1395":"1395","1393":"1393","1382":"1382","1429":"1429","Wolverton, Buckinghamshire, England":"Wolverton, Buckinghamshire, England","Westmorland, England":"Westmorland, England","Preston Patrick, Westmorland, England":"Preston Patrick, Westmorland, England","Hickleton, Yorkshire, England, United Kingdom":"Hickleton, Yorkshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1393–1435":"1393–1435","1395–1435":"1395–1435","1382–1429":"1382–1429","1431–1523":"1431–1523","1434–Male":"1434–Kuollut","1414–1459":"1414–1459","1459":"1459","1403":"1403","1414":"1414","1435":"1435","1523":"1523","1434":"1434","1431":"1431","1395":"1395","1393":"1393","1382":"1382","1429":"1429","Wolverton, Buckinghamshire, England":"Wolverton, Buckinghamshire, England","Westmorland, England":"Westmorland, England","Preston Patrick, Westmorland, England":"Preston Patrick, Westmorland, England","Hickleton, Yorkshire, England, United Kingdom":"Hickleton, Yorkshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1393–1435":"1393–1435","1395–1435":"1395–1435","1382–1429":"1382–1429","1431–1523":"1431–1523","1434–Male":"1434–Décédé","1414–1459":"1414–1459","1459":"1459","1403":"1403","1414":"1414","1435":"1435","1523":"1523","1434":"1434","1431":"1431","1395":"1395","1393":"1393","1382":"1382","1429":"1429","Wolverton, Buckinghamshire, England":"Wolverton, Buckinghamshire, Angleterre","Westmorland, England":"Westmorland, Angleterre","Preston Patrick, Westmorland, England":"Preston Patrick,